name: Vector Textures.
description:
This vector set of over 20 objects was built to combine the tangible elements of brushes, ink, palette knives and textures into your work. It's all about incorporating physical marks into a digital process.

These vectors are royalty free and for you to use as you see fit. But you MAY NOT tweak and re-sell.

All sales of downloaded files are final and there are no refunds on purchased downloads.

After payment, you will receive the file by email within 24 hours, sent directly to the address used with payment.
